As for the titles automatically given I'm going to suggest a modified version of my original proposal, I've added the space tourist rank in and also changed the pilot, commander and captain ranks to specifly mention nuclear powered ships.  I don't think there will be many people getting up to Federation President.<br>
<br>
TV Watcher (1 - 10)<br>
Space Cadet (11 - 25)<br>
Space Tourist (26 - 50)<br>
Astronaut (51 - 100)<br>
NTR Spaceship Pilot (101 - 150)<br>
Orion Commander (151 - 250)<br>
Fusion Starship Captain (251 - 500)<br>
Colony Governor (501 - 1000)<br>
Federation President (1001 - Infinity)<br>
<br>
